## 2. 백엔드

### 2-1. `WatchlistRepository.kt` 신규 생성

`backend/src/main/kotlin/com/jumisa/repository/WatchlistRepository.kt`

- `findItemsByMember(memberId, sort)` — watchlist JOIN stock + LATERAL undervalue_score + LATERAL stock_price_snapshot
- sort: `recent`(w.created_at DESC) / `price`(current_price DESC) / `rate`(change_rate DESC) / `score`(total_score DESC)
- `add` / `remove` — on conflict do nothing

### 2-2. `WatchlistController.kt` 신규 생성

`backend/src/main/kotlin/com/jumisa/controller/WatchlistController.kt`

- `GET /api/watchlist?sort=recent` → `{ items: List<ScreenerItem> }`
- `POST /api/watchlist/{stockCode}` → 추가
- `DELETE /api/watchlist/{stockCode}` → 제거

SecurityConfig 건드리지 않음 — `.anyRequest().authenticated()`로 이미 보호됨.

